{"id": 2226, "genre": 1000, "title": "现如今你都通过哪些方式自我科普？", "description": "除了课本，你的科学素养都是从哪儿来的？欢迎在留言区补充（题图来自：视觉中国）", "record_count": 15485, "comment_count": 25, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201803141436309ASdz2gj7cZOnIGY.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-03-15T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 3855, "title": "现如今你都通过哪些方式自我科普？", "content": "现如今，你都是通过哪些方式自我科普的？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 270708, "content": "定向接收型，关注了喜欢的果壳作者、科普博主/公众号", "image": "img/option/option/201803151702290K3615HQAUJs7yLM.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 270709, "content": "新闻突发型，诺贝尔颁奖/重要科学家去世时会去留心", "image": "img/option/option/2018031517300986ys3UDdrFOkoeiz.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 270711, "content": "需求驱动型，买护肤品/健身/生病了就会去钻研看看", "image": "img/option/option/20180315173628FXGbljDO5VuSiAI2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 270716, "content": "正经学术型，权威的科技期刊长期追随着", "image": "img/option/option/20180315183747vgxGU2QldpE6Tfsy.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 270513, "content": "记录片型，制作精良的纪录片可以说是我的第三只眼睛了", "image": "img/option/option/20180315162644D5vxMi4upkjat3gr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 270514, "content": "公开课型，看不看得完是一回事，我好学的心日月可鉴", "image": "img/option/option/20180314145220rzyhBEw3lcVMY7PK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 270516, "content": "逛知乎型，刷到一个好问题和好答案是种怎样的体验", "image": "img/option/option/20180314145731X4Kgm861WGFpNHvn.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 270521, "content": "经验型，总之先重启试试", "image": "img/option/option/20180314150309RrQVM7NUqSpoEgXB.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 270522, "content": "辟谣型，看到爸妈发来的科普贴先反对再去找证据", "image": "img/option/option/20180314150532mtcylgdT9QjsYkXe.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 270523, "content": "守株待兔型，随机刷到科普相关信息就点开看看", "image": "img/option/option/201803141508217yPk4hEoUIAs1jan.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 270524, "content": "灵光一闪型，突然想到“这是咋回事”就去搜资料", "image": "img/option/option/20180314151124DHtZ376pOlKs0Rvh.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 270525, "content": "动手实验型，哈？真的吗，让我试试看", "image": "img/option/option/20180314151245xLypW5Y8Mb4rq3wl.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}